{"tid":243612,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"［深夜抒情］祈禱你的二十歲是快樂的。雖然我的二十歲早已悽慘地過完😶","createTime":"2017-05-14T18:43:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-14T18:46:00.000Z","uid":116429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6edc31fc04c2b453c4cc94d36b784e558a682659","tid":243612,"uid":116429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T18:43:05.000Z","msg":"「我祈禱你的二十歲是快樂的。雖然我的二十歲似乎快要悽慘地過完了，不過如果你能連我的份也一起快樂度過的話，我就很高興了。真的。」<br />\n<br />\n直子 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點解我嘅二十歲會有你嘅影子架<br />\n<br />\n唔知你地嘅二十歲又過得快樂嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不論係快樂定悽慘都可以係度分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d338cf205d58d4b4b45d6b1e9f609e43c94ecf3","tid":243612,"uid":93720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T18:46:00.000Z","msg":"雖然二十歲未到<br />\n但呢個十八歲過得一啲都唔開心"}]}